Plot:

Infamous New Jersey killer Richard Kuklinski, charged with over 100 murders, speaks candidly about himself and the grisly murders he committed over decades for the mob. Kuklinski was so cold-blooded and merciless that he earned the nickname "Iceman." 
Hear him describe his killings and family life.
